    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean i know i should ask them but i can't get an appointment for like two weeks and i'm literally exhausted. it's not like they're both dangerous drugs or anything right? melatonin is just a supplement. wouldn't they just kind of work together to help me sleep better? i just want to know if it's actually dangerous or if it's just a standard thing people do.",
